      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       dic-ini-pgm-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Sigla funzione                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "P+"                 to   s-ope                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Sistema applicativo                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      i-ide-sap            to   s-sap                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
